563
564        if ($command->getId() === -1) {

568            $commandId = $command->getId();
569        }

573                [
574                    ':id'           => $commandId,
575                    ':test_id'      => $testId,
576                    ':keyword'      => $command->getKeyword(),
577                    ':parameter'    => json_encode($command->getArguments()),
578                    ':commander_id' => $commanderId,
579                    ':timestamp'    => TimeStamp::toSQLFormat($command->getTimestamp())
580                ]);
581
582        return $commandId;
